  "keyFeatures": [
    "Zero-config installation with automatic ADB setup",
    "Cross-platform support (Windows, Linux, macOS, Android/Termux)",
    "Decryption of crypt12, crypt14, and crypt15 databases",
    "Automated backup extraction via ADB",
    "Interactive chat viewer with SQLite parsing",
    "Multi-format export (HTML, CSV, JSON, TXT)",
    "Media file extraction and linking",
    "Encrypted key storage with machine-specific encryption"
